  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WASTE</h2> is a retro, pseudo 3D RPG where you take on the role of a Dustbin / Garbage man, collecting WASTE from the houses <br>of the street you are working on, avoiding obstacles like cars, bikes, dogs, etc, if you are efficient and keep off the grass, your customer is happy and they <br>will invite you inside to play on their new computer or ask favours to earn more money. <br>Each street has a time limit, so you cant waste time, the faster you are, the more money you get, and your gaffer is happy.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME FEATURES:</h2></strong><br><strong>Fast paced obsticle dodging action.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/983de943e5621ff9fd0a3c7d565e7e65.poster.avif?t=1658509305\" width=476 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/983de943e5621ff9fd0a3c7d565e7e65.webm?t=1658509305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/983de943e5621ff9fd0a3c7d565e7e65.mp4?t=1658509305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul><strong>Rough areas have extreme obsticles.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/f89e6e8d0f77888f6d512af5c389f305.poster.avif?t=1658509305\" width=480 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/f89e6e8d0f77888f6d512af5c389f305.webm?t=1658509305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/f89e6e8d0f77888f6d512af5c389f305.mp4?t=1658509305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul><strong>Do requests from happy customers to earn more money.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/7f0cc709974f4b8b4c1a7a0fa02d7d82.poster.avif?t=1658509305\" width=480 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/7f0cc709974f4b8b4c1a7a0fa02d7d82.webm?t=1658509305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/7f0cc709974f4b8b4c1a7a0fa02d7d82.mp4?t=1658509305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WASTE</h2> is a retro, pseudo 3D RPG where you take on the role of a Dustbin / Garbage man, collecting WASTE from the houses <br>of the street you are working on, avoiding obstacles like cars, bikes, dogs, etc, if you are efficient and keep off the grass, your customer is happy and they <br>will invite you inside to play on their new computer or ask favours to earn more money. <br>Each street has a time limit, so you cant waste time, the faster you are, the more money you get, and your gaffer is happy.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME FEATURES:</h2></strong><br><strong>Fast paced obsticle dodging action.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/983de943e5621ff9fd0a3c7d565e7e65.poster.avif?t=1658509305\" width=476 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/983de943e5621ff9fd0a3c7d565e7e65.webm?t=1658509305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/983de943e5621ff9fd0a3c7d565e7e65.mp4?t=1658509305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul><strong>Rough areas have extreme obsticles.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/f89e6e8d0f77888f6d512af5c389f305.poster.avif?t=1658509305\" width=480 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/f89e6e8d0f77888f6d512af5c389f305.webm?t=1658509305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885370/extras/f89e6e8d0f77888f6d512af5c389f305.mp4?t=1658509305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></vide